+ IT(jetty-war-test-failing) Unsupported major.minor version 51.0 (fixed in PR#76)&lt;br/&gt;
+ comment out @Override on interfaces in MarkAsFailureListener.java, see TODO comment and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-1130&quot; title=&quot;Remove TODO and deprecated code in surefire 3.0&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SUREFIRE-1130&quot;&gt;SUREFIRE-1130&lt;/a&gt; (fixed in PR#76)&lt;br/&gt;
+ remove unnecessary javac 1.6 in IT test surefire-1055-parallelTestCount/pom.xml (fixed in PR#76)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
